bcl:definition.bcl:text:
inspector means a person appointed as an inspector under
  section
  13;

bcl:paragraph.bcl:text:
a term or condition of registration under this Act, including, without
              limitation, terms and conditions described in section 11 and terms and
              conditions imposed on the registration by the registrar;

respecting the period of time, manner and form in which information must be
              provided to the local police authority for the purposes of section
              6;

exempting, on any conditions, for any periods of time and in any circumstances
              that are considered advisable, any transaction or class of transactions, or person or
              class of persons, from all or any part of this Act or the regulations;
